    </td><td><br /><strong>Who to Send:</strong><br />Plan to send members of your professional staff who will be most integral to the implementation of your mandatory education program. Please do not send individuals who will not be directly involved in implementation of the education program. <br /><br />
    <strong>Materials to Bring:</strong>
          <br /><ul>    
    <li>Your current strategic plan as it relates to your comprehensive prevention education program</li>
